text: Daniel Bartlett may refer to: *Daniel Bartlett (footballer) (born 2000), English footballer *Dan Bartlett (born 1971), counselor to the President during the George W. Bush administration *Daniel Bartlett, namesake of the Daniel and Esther Bartlett House, a historic house in Connecticut that is listed in the National Register of Historic Places ==See also== *Daniel Bartlett Allyn (born 1959), U.S. Army general *Daniel Bartlett Stevens (1837–1924), American politician and member of the Wisconsin State Assembly
title: Daniel Bartlett
